data.description: Beautiful stucco/stone 4BR/2.5BA two story family home in Hickory Shadow just minutes from Panther Creek State Park. Upgraded kitchen cabinets, granite tops and stainless appliances. Nearly 3/4 acre lot with fenced in back yard. Freshly painted interior and new carpet in bedrooms. Main level bonus room with separate outside entrance for home office, art or exercise studio, screened in covered patio and newer deck for outdoor entertaining with family/friends! Sellers have quote for new main level floors but timing for install was too far out. Offering $7000 flooring credit with full price offer.
